summary: Finally The Puppet Master Is Completed! New Dwelling, New Bosses, Good Loot!
descriptionHtml:
Update 2.1*
Extended the dwelling abit and placed a new companion mage Zen to the exit of the extended dwelling! She will lvl up with you up to lvl 80. Also extended lair is a place you can use as a house very convenient, Keep in mind this is still being extended and I will be implementing more fixes. PLEASE ENDORSE THIS FILE IF YOU ENJOY IT!

Be Wary Traveler\'s The Daedric Gods are pissed off and unleashing more Demon\'s in Skyrim.
Puppets this time around and I don\'t mean toys! These puppets mean business and the Puppet Master is sitting back and laughing as they wreak havok on Skyrim.

Features
*New Bosses
*New Mobs
*New Dwelling
*GOOD loot

I suggest to be at or around at least lvl 20 to attempt this boss.
The Puppet\'s Lair is on a small island just outside of Solitude see pics for map!
Let me know your thoughts or any bugs you may find. I do not suggest using any kind of Manniquin mods with this mod! If you enjoy it please Endorse me and Vote, I will create much more mods in future if i see people care.
This is my newest boss mod check it out!
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10970
